data.description: Welcome to your dream home - with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths & 2043 sq ft of living space there's ample room for your family to grow and flourish. Step into the spacious kitchen with granite counters and a pantry fit for a chef. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining area, and family room, creating the perfect space for entertaining. Upstairs, you'll find a loft, ideal for a home office or play area. The master suite features a large shower & plenty of closet space.  Enjoy the privacy of a fenced backyard on this wooded lot, perfect for relaxing on the patio. Located in the highly desirable DD2 school district this home has everything you need. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Plus, the seller is offering a $2,500 paint allowance with an acceptable offer.
